author: THOMAS BEAUMONT
title: Cruz raps 2016 rival Rubio for skipping Senate debates
text:
Joaquin slowing down and getting ready to turn to the North on Friday 
Miami - Joaquin may be going through an eyewall replacement. This usually happens with major hurricanes where the storm goes through a cycle where it develops another band of strong storms around the inner core of the storm. This may only be a temporary trend as warm waters and little shear still exist in the path of this storm for the next 24 hours.
